Teste01.query:
SELECT
  CS.ad_id,
  CS.impressions AS Impressions,
  CS.advertiser_name AS Advertiser,
  CONCAT("https://adstransparency.google.com/advertiser/", CS.advertiser_id, "/creative/", CS.ad_id, "?political=&region=") AS Creative_Page,
FROM
  `bigquery-public-data.google_political_ads.creative_stats` AS CS
WHERE
  CS.impressions = "1000000-1250000"
  OR CS.impressions = "1250000-1500000"
  OR CS.impressions = "1500000-1750000"
  OR CS.impressions = "1750000-2000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "2000000-2250000"
  OR CS.impressions = "2250000-2500000"
  OR CS.impressions = "2500000-3000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "3000000-3500000"
  OR CS.impressions = "3500000-4000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "4000000-4500000"
  OR CS.impressions = "4500000-5000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "5000000-6000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "6000000-7000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "7000000-8000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "8000000-9000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "9000000-10000000"
  OR CS.impressions = "â‰¥10000000";
